Spokane 32 partly cloudy.
   _INTERNATIONAL: Calgary 43 partly cloudy; Montreal 50 hazy;
Ottawa 50 fair; Regina 19 fair; Toronto 41 foggy; Winnipeg 27
partly cloudy.
