<TEXT>
   A parachutist fell to his death when his
chute failed to open over this northeastern Alabama town.
   David Lee, 29, of nearby Jacksonville, Ala., was killed
instantly about 1:20 p.m. Sunday when he fell into a field adjacent
to the McMinn Airport in Weaver, Calhoun County Coroner Ralph
